headline: Jefferies Lifts EOG Resources (EOG) Price Target, Keeps Buy Rating
summary: EOG Resources, Inc. (NYSE:EOG) is one of the 10 Best Oil and Gas Stocks to Buy Now. On June 13, Jefferies increased its price target on EOG Resources, Inc. (NYSE:EOG) from $144 to $148 while keeping a “Buy” rating. This decision came after discussions with EOG Resources, Inc.’s (NYSE:EOG) Vice President and Head of Investor […]
